name: PresentationFUEL
overview:
PresentationFUEL Ltd., a privately held, Copenhagen-based graphic design and production company, was organized in 2008 to develop affordably priced graphic design solutions for producing professionally designed PowerPoint presentations. Customers are able to produce their presentations for a fraction of the cost and time previously required.

Using the PresentationFUELs website, the customer simply selects a presentation template, purchases and downloads it, then customizes the layout thereby creating a professional presentation.

The customizable templates are created and produced by award-winning graphic designers and seasoned production artists. The companyâ€™s products include royalty-free stock photos and original artwork.
